{"tid":1606922,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(決定！) 港島定六區？","createTime":"2019-09-30T16:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T18:32:54.000Z","uid":22873,"like":43,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"eeb443d2f5fb55dad50235f213ca08183bbea7d4","tid":1606922,"uid":22873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:36:27.000Z","msg":"雖然時間唔多，但大家好無再諗下係六區定港島？一齊討論下利弊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">六區</span>會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">分散手足</span>，八月五號已經試過，感覺上安全啲易走啲？(不過我地目標唔係逃跑)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港島</span>可以集中手足，啲狗要搞你都難啲，但所有商場會閂哂，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">補給同避都難</span>。同埋民陣同長毛嗰啲一開始都決定係港島，我諗佢地都係覺得好啲先有呢個決策。宜家仲出嚟叫大家去港島，俾人拉硬都想大家出港島，係咪去港島好啲？<br />\n<br />\n大家真係一齊分析下，唔好收手足分太散。其實之前講過好多次，<span style=\"color: red;\">愈多人就愈安全</span>，如果唔係勇武唔洗和理非back up啦。警方封得港島禁勁，係咪佢地都淆先咁做？<br />\n<br />\n港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n六區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n賀佢老母！</span>"},{"pid":"04292174b9f598e51b67d52824f36b80ee296db1","tid":1606922,"uid":140492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十一革命 撥亂反正</span></span>"},{"pid":"a3c5d6c3f23d15e67f9d657dd14cdb1fb7c624e4","tid":1606922,"uid":22873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:38:31.000Z","msg":"大家一齊分析下啦"},{"pid":"7d942a417ebcedc67d87f214aa030a66590a1f42","tid":1606922,"uid":302542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"c108ac255d9f92956925f059f4e94167f6a1fb36","tid":1606922,"uid":22873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:42:04.000Z","msg":"我諗得唔全面，所以想大家都一齊俾下意見。<br />\n唔係人話六區就六區，港島就港島，係大家點諗。"},{"pid":"926f01e1676f7e31ed0c22b49c285f30728c651a","tid":16